'''Aɣyul''', d aɣersiw i yellan s waṭas deg umaḍal, mecṭuḥ s-ddaw n usardun akk d uɛawdiw, imeẓẓuɣen-is d imeqṛanen. Aṭas n ccetlat n yiɣyal i yellan deg umaḍal, maca win yettwasnen aṭas gar-asen d aɣyul aqeddac (âne domestique s tefṛansist) i d-yekkan s usegred n weɣyul azagir (âne sauvage).

==Tamawalt==

Amalay : Aɣyul.

Unti : Taɣyult.

Aɣyul amecṭuḥ isem-is : Ajḥiḥ.

Asuɣu-ines qqaṛen-as jjaɛwat, ijaɛɛu, tjaɛɛu, jaɛɛun, jaɛɛunt (Md: Sliɣ i waɣyul '''ijaɛu''').

Ilaq ad nesemgarad gar waɣyul akked usardun (mmi-s n weɣyul akked tegmart neɣ taɛawdiwt).

Awal-agi "Aɣyul" deg tutlayt '''tamaziɣt taqbaylit''', yesɛa ugar n yiwwen unamek, Iqbayliyen mmalen-d s-yes : aɣyul (aɣersiw), amdan ur yeḥṛicen ara neɣ amdan i yesɛan tazmert (yezmer ad yerfed aṭas ɣef tuyat-is).

